            "body": "<p><a href=\"https://stleary.github.io/JSON-java/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://stleary.github.io/JSON-java/<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>One library a day, keeps StackOverflow away.<\/p>\n\n<p>Usage:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>JSONObject jo = new JSONObject(response);\n\n// get all keys\njo.keys();\n\n// values\nfor (String key: jo.keys()) {\n    jo.get(key);\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
