            "body": "<p>You can use Gson library<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>class Data {\n  Vulnerability vulnerability\n}\n\nclass Vulnerability {\n  long id;\n  String status;\n... }\n\nData data = new Gson().fromJson(yourString, Data.class);\nSystem.out.println(data.vulnerability.status);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
